data.description: Newly remodeled Quad multifamily 8 bed, 4 bath apartment building for sale. Located steps from the Golden Belt Campus and within walking distance to downtown Durham. The total building square footage is 3819. Each unit is 955 square feet and features 2 Bedrooms and 1 full bathroom. Primary Bedroom has large walk-in closet and add'l closet. Each unit has in-unit washer and dryer. Updated kitchens and bathrooms, fresh paint, tile backsplash, microwaves and new bamboo flooring. The exterior of the building has been refreshed and the backyard has been completely fenced in with locked access. Roof installed in 2021.  High rental potential in this rapidly growing area of Durham.
